{"tid":2224302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[亮J]支那據報準備對Google發起反壟斷調查","createTime":"2020-09-30T11:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T15:07:53.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ed35cec1d64441ebfb124d6779cb397327611ae4","tid":2224302,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552504-20200930.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552504-20200930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyjcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=29e4234f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552504-20200930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8f64f64f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552504-20200930.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國據報準備對Google發起反壟斷調查，調查有關Google利用Android系統的優勢，妨礙競爭的指控。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述知情人士報道，調查案是由中國電訊設備商華為在去年提出，中國反壟斷監管機構已提交給國務院審核，當局最快在10月決定是否展開調查，而有關決定可能受到中美關係的影響。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士又說，當局亦可能會調查Google的市場地位，是否可能對華為等中國企業，造成極大損害的指控，因為失去這間美國科技巨頭對Andriod系統的支持，會導致信心喪失和收入下降。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你個蒙撚OS都係用AOSP，連AOSP都ban鳩埋你用返飛鴿傳書都得勒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c310a2ce40a20629d209d971a7b694e64f9e6465","tid":2224302,"uid":144626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"人地個網都俾你封左，點壟斷你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7461f81fe45e5513860815cce452a94965a2b927","tid":2224302,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0